# Market Data

> Full policy in `.ai/context/market-data.md`.

- Provider files under `market_data/providers/` are API blackboxes — no Celery/views imports.
- Orchestration goes through `market_data/services/` (`get_daily_data`, symbol resolution, validation).
- Never call provider blackboxes from views/tasks directly.
